    RTC Test Case Description:
  
  
System must not allow a user to change the interest rate during the term of CD at the account level if &quot;No Rate change allowed during the term of the CD (M: Up to maturity)&quot; is selected at the product level. And system must throw an error that is &quot; Interest Rate change is not allowed. No rate change allowed till maturity.&quot;
Success Criteria: System did not allow a user to change the interest rate. And throws an error.


  
